Things to deprecate for Curv 0.6

* 'f x: x + 1' style fields
* 'fields' (see Collection)
* 'local' definitions (see Definition)
* imperative generators
* deprecate 'log n' for 'ln n'
* deprecate 'amend' for 'set' (see Index)

Things to report as an error (for one release, before new syntax comes in).

* a[i] -- array indexing
* !a   -- not
